> Perceptor quickly came in and started to search rodimus.

As perceptor came in there were a few changes in the room. Rodimus, Cyclonus and Scourge were now awake inside thier recharge pods. Rodimus looked angry, Scourge looked like he were about to rip out of his, but could not, and Cyclonus looked around calmly. "Perceptor." Cyclonus' spoke in a harsh whisper, "You must free all of us!" He paused and then continued, "Zarak, the controller of Scorponok must be freed as well. It is he who opened the door. He won't maintain control for long."

Meanwhile Rodimus struggled a bit, "Hurry up and get me out of this!"

(TAG: Perceptor)


> Darkfate tought a second meditating what he heard. at last he said 
> looking towards Rodimus and the others bots "What will we do with 
> Those bots, Malik?"

The self proclaimed Marauder frowned slightly at Darkfate and then looked upward, "We are changing plans." He clenched his fist. "This base will no longer serve my needs. It will destroyed, along with those others."

Marauder looked back at Darkfate, "Gather yourselves, we leave momentarilly!"

(TAG: Darkfate)
